- BridgeEventRelay: 11 NotificationCenter observers for workspace/pane/
  surface events (selected, created, closed, title_changed, split, focused,
  moved) pushed to connected bridge clients as JSON
- Surface lifecycle cleanup: BridgePTYStream observes surface.closed to
  release observer contexts and prevent use-after-free

